itemLabel: Peter Bennett, 1st Baron Bennett of Edgbaston

wikipedia_page.main: Peter Frederick Blaker Bennett, 1st Baron Bennett of Edgbaston, OBE, JP (16 April 1880 – 27 September 1957), known as Sir Peter Bennett between 1941 and 1953, was a British businessman and Conservative Party politician.
